Title: mknotifyd did not always reload its configuration
Level: 1
Component: notifications
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.5.0i1
Date: 1496914391

The mknotifyd did not automatically detect changes, when they were configured
through the site specific global settings in the distributed monitoring page.
A restart of the mknotifyd was required.
